description: Chill out with "Trash Punk: Winter Rampage"! This DLC brings a wintry twist to the familiar world of "Trash Punk." Wander through the chaotic levels, now covered in a blanket of snow and ice. The change of scenery adds a fresh visual flavor to your favorite maps, giving a new look to your punk-rock rebellion. Perfect for players who enjoy aesthetic change to spice up their gameplay!
name: Trash Punk - DLC#1 Winter Rampage
